{"tha-ap540:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap540:0.2":"Kaccayanavagga ","tha-ap540:0.3":"8 Uruvelakassapattheraapadana ","tha-ap540:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap540:1.2":"sabbalokavidu muni; ","tha-ap540:1.3":"Ito satasahassamhi, ","tha-ap540:1.4":"kappe uppajji cakkhuma. ","tha-ap540:2.1":"Ovadako vinnapako, ","tha-ap540:2.2":"tarako sabbapaninam; ","tha-ap540:2.3":"Desanakusalo buddho, ","tha-ap540:2.4":"taresi janatam bahum. ","tha-ap540:3.1":"Anukampako karuniko, ","tha-ap540:3.2":"hitesi sabbapaninam; ","tha-ap540:3.3":"Sampatte titthiye sabbe, ","tha-ap540:3.4":"pancasile patitthapi. ","tha-ap540:4.1":"Evam nirakulam asi, ","tha-ap540:4.2":"sunnatam titthiyehi ca; ","tha-ap540:4.3":"Vicittam arahantehi, ","tha-ap540:4.4":"vasibhutehi tadibhi. ","tha-ap540:5.1":"Ratananatthapannasam, ","tha-ap540:5.2":"uggato so mahamuni; ","tha-ap540:5.3":"Kancanagghiyasankaso, ","tha-ap540:5.4":"battimsavaralakkhano. ","tha-ap540:6.1":"Vassasatasahassani, ","tha-ap540:6.2":"ayu vijjati tavade; ","tha-ap540:6.3":"Tavata titthamano so, ","tha-ap540:6.4":"taresi janatam bahum. ","tha-ap540:7.1":"Tadaham hamsavatiya, ","tha-ap540:7.2":"brahmano sadhusammato; ","tha-ap540:7.3":"Upecca lokapajjotam, ","tha-ap540:7.4":"assosim dhammadesanam. ","tha-ap540:8.1":"Tada mahaparisatim, ","tha-ap540:8.2":"mahaparisasavakam; ","tha-ap540:8.3":"Thapentam etadaggamhi, ","tha-ap540:8.4":"sutvana mudito aham. ","tha-ap540:9.1":"Mahata parivarena, ","tha-ap540:9.2":"nimantetva mahajinam; ","tha-ap540:9.3":"Brahmananam sahassena, ","tha-ap540:9.4":"sahadanamadasaham. ","tha-ap540:10.1":"Mahadanam daditvana, ","tha-ap540:10.2":"abhivadiya nayakam; ","tha-ap540:10.3":"Ekamantam thito hattho, ","tha-ap540:10.4":"idam vacanamabravim. ","tha-ap540:11.1":"‘Tayi saddhaya me vira, ","tha-ap540:11.2":"adhikaragunena ca; ","tha-ap540:11.3":"Parisa mahati hotu, ","tha-ap540:11.4":"nibbattassa tahim tahim’. ","tha-ap540:12.1":"Tada avoca parisam, ","tha-ap540:12.2":"gajagajjitasussaro; ","tha-ap540:12.3":"Karavikaruto sattha, ","tha-ap540:12.4":"‘etam passatha brahmanam. ","tha-ap540:13.1":"Hemavannam mahabahum, ","tha-ap540:13.2":"kamalananalocanam; ","tha-ap540:13.3":"Udaggatanujam hattham, ","tha-ap540:13.4":"saddhavantam gune mama. ","tha-ap540:14.1":"Esa patthayate thanam, ","tha-ap540:14.2":"sihaghosassa bhikkhuno; ","tha-ap540:14.3":"Anagatamhi addhane, ","tha-ap540:14.4":"lacchase tam manoratham. ","tha-ap540:15.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap540:15.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap540:15.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap540:15.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap540:16.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap540:16.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap540:16.3":"Kassapo nama gottena, ","tha-ap540:16.4":"hessati satthu savako’. ","tha-ap540:17.1":"Ito dvenavute kappe, ","tha-ap540:17.2":"ahu sattha anuttaro; ","tha-ap540:17.3":"Anupamo asadiso, ","tha-ap540:17.4":"phusso lokagganayako. ","tha-ap540:18.1":"So ca sabbam tamam hantva, ","tha-ap540:18.2":"vijatetva mahajatam; ","tha-ap540:18.3":"Vassate amatam vutthim, ","tha-ap540:18.4":"tappayanto sadevakam. ","tha-ap540:19.1":"Tada hi baranasiyam, ","tha-ap540:19.2":"raja pacca ahumhase; ","tha-ap540:19.3":"Bhataromha tayo sabbe, ","tha-ap540:19.4":"samvisatthava rajino. ","tha-ap540:20.1":"Virangarupa balino, ","tha-ap540:20.2":"sangame aparajita; ","tha-ap540:20.3":"Tada kupitapaccanto, ","tha-ap540:20.4":"amhe aha mahipati. ","tha-ap540:21.1":"‘Etha gantvana paccantam, ","tha-ap540:21.2":"sodhetva attavibalam; ","tha-ap540:21.3":"Khemam vijiritam katva, ","tha-ap540:21.4":"puna dethati bhasatha’. ","tha-ap540:22.1":"Tato mayam avocumha, ","tha-ap540:22.2":"yadi deyyasi nayakam; ","tha-ap540:22.3":"Upatthanaya amhakam, ","tha-ap540:22.4":"sadhayissama vo tato. ","tha-ap540:23.1":"Tato mayam laddhavara, ","tha-ap540:23.2":"bhumipalena pesita; ","tha-ap540:23.3":"Nikkhittasattham paccantam, ","tha-ap540:23.4":"katva punarupacca tam. ","tha-ap540:24.1":"Yacitva satthupatthanam, ","tha-ap540:24.2":"rajanam lokanayakam; ","tha-ap540:24.3":"Muniviram labhitvana, ","tha-ap540:24.4":"yavajivam yajimha tam. ","tha-ap540:25.1":"Mahagghani ca vatthani, ","tha-ap540:25.2":"panitani rasani ca; ","tha-ap540:25.3":"Senasanani rammani, ","tha-ap540:25.4":"bhesajjani hitani ca. ","tha-ap540:26.1":"Datva sasanghamunino, ","tha-ap540:26.2":"dhammenuppaditani no; ","tha-ap540:26.3":"Silavanto karunika, ","tha-ap540:26.4":"bhavanayuttamanasa. ","tha-ap540:27.1":"Saddha paricaritvana, ","tha-ap540:27.2":"mettacittena nayakam; ","tha-ap540:27.3":"Nibbute tamhi lokagge, ","tha-ap540:27.4":"pujam katva yathabalam. ","tha-ap540:28.1":"Tato cuta santusitam, ","tha-ap540:28.2":"gata tattha mahasukham; ","tha-ap540:28.3":"Anubhuta mayam sabbe, ","tha-ap540:28.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap540:29.1":"Mayakaro yatha range, ","tha-ap540:29.2":"dassesi vikatim bahum; ","tha-ap540:29.3":"Tatha bhave bhamantoham, ","tha-ap540:29.4":"videhadhipati ahum. ","tha-ap540:30.1":"Gunacelassa vakyena, ","tha-ap540:30.2":"micchaditthigatasayo; ","tha-ap540:30.3":"Narakam maggamarulho, ","tha-ap540:30.4":"rucaya mama dhituya. ","tha-ap540:31.1":"Ovadam nadiyitvana, ","tha-ap540:31.2":"brahmuna naradenaham; ","tha-ap540:31.3":"Bahudha samsito santo, ","tha-ap540:31.4":"ditthim hitvana papikam. ","tha-ap540:32.1":"Purayitva visesena, ","tha-ap540:32.2":"dasa kammapathaniham; ","tha-ap540:32.3":"Hitvana dehamagamim, ","tha-ap540:32.4":"saggam sabhavanam yatha. ","tha-ap540:33.1":"Pacchime bhave sampatte, ","tha-ap540:33.2":"brahmabandhu ahosaham; ","tha-ap540:33.3":"Baranasiyam phitayam, ","tha-ap540:33.4":"jato vippamahakule. ","tha-ap540:34.1":"Maccubyadhijara bhito, ","tha-ap540:34.2":"ogahetva mahavanam; ","tha-ap540:34.3":"Nibbanam padamesanto, ","tha-ap540:34.4":"jatilesu paribbajim. ","tha-ap540:35.1":"Tada dve bhataro mayham, ","tha-ap540:35.2":"pabbajimsu maya saha; ","tha-ap540:35.3":"Uruvelayam mapetva, ","tha-ap540:35.4":"assamam nivasim aham. ","tha-ap540:36.1":"Kassapo nama gottena, ","tha-ap540:36.2":"uruvelanivasiko; ","tha-ap540:36.3":"Tato me asi pannatti, ","tha-ap540:36.4":"uruvelakassapo iti. ","tha-ap540:37.1":"Nadisakase bhata me, ","tha-ap540:37.2":"nadikassapasavhayo; ","tha-ap540:37.3":"Asi sakasanamena, ","tha-ap540:37.4":"gayayam gayakassapo. ","tha-ap540:38.1":"Dve satani kanitthassa, ","tha-ap540:38.2":"tini majjhassa bhatuno; ","tha-ap540:38.3":"Mama panca satanuna, ","tha-ap540:38.4":"sissa sabbe mamanuga. ","tha-ap540:39.1":"Tada upecca mam buddho, ","tha-ap540:39.2":"katvana vividhani me; ","tha-ap540:39.3":"Patihirani lokaggo, ","tha-ap540:39.4":"vinesi narasarathi. ","tha-ap540:40.1":"Sahassaparivarena, ","tha-ap540:40.2":"ahosim ehibhikkhuko; ","tha-ap540:40.3":"Teheva saha sabbehi, ","tha-ap540:40.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","tha-ap540:41.1":"Te cevanne ca bahavo, ","tha-ap540:41.2":"sissa mam parivarayum; ","tha-ap540:41.3":"Sasitunca samatthoham, ","tha-ap540:41.4":"tato mam isisattamo. ","tha-ap540:42.1":"Mahaparisabhavasmim, ","tha-ap540:42.2":"etadagge thapesi mam; ","tha-ap540:42.3":"Aho buddhe katam karam, ","tha-ap540:42.4":"saphalam me ajayatha. ","tha-ap540:43.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap540:43.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap540:43.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap540:44.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap540:44.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap540:44.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap540:45.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap540:45.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap540:45.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap540:46.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma uruvelakassapo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap540:47.1":"Uruvelakassapattherassapadanam atthamam. "}